            "content": "tangent of {@code this}.",
            "assertion": "assert methodResultID.equals(new Complex( FastMath.sin(2*receiverObjectID.getReal())/(FastMath.cos(2*receiverObjectID.getReal())+receiverObjectID.cosh(2*receiverObjectID.getImaginary())), receiverObjectID.sinh(2*receiverObjectID.getImaginary())/(FastMath.cos(2*receiverObjectID.getReal())+receiverObjectID.cosh(2*receiverObjectID.getImaginary())) ));",
